@startuml 06_CICD_Pipeline
!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft JhengHei"
title CI/CD Pipeline 流程圖

|Developer|
start
:Git Push (main);

|GitHub Actions|
:程式碼 Linting\n與靜態掃描;
:執行整合測試\n(Maven Test);
:容器打包\n(Docker Build);
:推送映像檔\n(Push to Artifact Registry);

|GCP 部署環境|
:部署至 Cloud Run;
:注入憑證與環境變數;
note right
  Cloud SQL
  Redis
  環境 Secrets
end note
stop

@enduml
